<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能散发傲人的光辉对吧？！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />与生俱来的才能自然是必要的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但要是不坚持努力的话，
绝对成不了真正的偶像～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在<delay20 />一点都不想
