再说什么了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感觉自己脑袋<delay20 />都要炸开了！<delay40 />
